query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(chn ci mc t) */ select min(chn.name) AS uncredited_voiced_character,
min(t.title) AS russian_movie
from char_name AS chn
inner join cast_info AS ci
on chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND ci.note like '%(voice)%' AND ci.note like '%(uncredited)%'
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
inner join title AS t
on t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2003;
